There was a sigh from WING CALIBER as he watched STRAIGHT SHOT and RAT
TRAP walk towards the medical bay. It would be a short while before
the medical staff returned from their trip retrieving SILVERBOLT and
TUSCON and then another while as they had to go back out and get the
rest of the FUZORS.

WING CALIBER turned to look at the PADD in his hand as he talked to
NIGHTSHIFT, "So who got the scan from Dark Rodimus? Is he still
holding the matrix?" CALIBER's voice had a knowing sound to it as he
probrably already knew that no one had yet. The PADD he was holding
had the current reports on it.

He turned to look at the shuttle as it was coming in for a landing the
bay door already opening. "Leo Prime I am sure will have a lot to to
discuss with everyone, as he will probrably want to hear everyone's
report first hand." WING CALIBER stowed his PADD in subspace as he
walked towards the shuttle.

"Perhaps you should take Elita to her chambers?" CALBER said as he
shook his head ruefully. "I believe that this debacle far from over. I
hope Tuscon is ready for it."

Already SANTON and BUMP could be seen hovering over SILVERBOLT as they
prepped to bring him in as the feeding tubes were retracting from
TUSCON - He could get more once they got him inside.

(TAG)

Preston
